Class ReplicationTypeIdentityProjection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.morpheusdata.model.MorpheusModel
      • com.morpheusdata.model.projection.ReplicationTypeIdentityProjection
  • public class ReplicationTypeIdentityProjection
extends MorpheusModel
    Provides a subset of properties from the ReplicationType object for doing a sync match comparison with less bandwidth usage and memory footprint. This is a DTO Projection object
